Stamford_Transportation_Center\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET on NBC and Peacock with \\\"Primetime in Paris,\\\" hosted byMike Tiricoand featuring in-depth storytelling and a cinematic main title sequence.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.3615243883810002e-11, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9998963788114713, \"rank\": 0.00010363192712259743, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3162202252220563e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On tonight's \\\"Primetime in Paris,\\\"Noah Lylesruns for the title of World's Fastest Man in the men's 100m,Suni Leecompetes in the women's uneven bar final, and Team USA contests the final day of swimming events on \\\"Primetime in Paris\\\" on NBC and Peacock beginning tonight at 7 p.m.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/100_metres\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.154855593646298e-35, \"text\": \"100m\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/100_metres\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/100_metres\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3162202252220563e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbped