ert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Monday's coverage is headlined by track & field action live at 1 p.m.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET on NBC and Peacock, highlighted by 200m American record holder and 2023 world champion Noah Lylescompeting in the first round of the men's 200m, Tokyo Olympic discus gold medalistValarie Allmanattempting to defend her gold medal, and finals in the women's 5,000m and 800m.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1718, \"end\": 1721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.3615243883810002e-11, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9998963788114713, \"rank\": 0.00010363192712259743, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996417734000538, \"rank\": 0.000358229846895515, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.8818251528463439, \"rank\": 0.13401125245522083, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}, {\"begin\"