Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}, {\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9998963788114713, \"rank\": 0.00010363192712259743, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickherefor more information on tomorrow's coverage.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"***  Following are highlights from today's coverage of the Paris Olympics on the platforms of NBCUniversal:  TRACK & FIELD  Ato Boldon on Noah Lyles winning the men's 100m: \\\"Noah Lyles did not win his heat, he did not win his semifinal, but he won the one that counted.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.776841011422084e-25, \"text\": \"Ato Boldon\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\"}, {\"begin\": 2945, \"end\": 2955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah Lyles is the Olympic champion and the United States have won gold [in the men's 100m] for the first time in 20 years!\\\"\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3077, \"end\": 3087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 3120, \"end\": 3133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999970698952165, \"rank\": 2.9172217855009733e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leigh Diffey on the photo finish of the men's 100m: \\\"It's Noah Lyles!\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3260, \"end\": 3270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it had to go to a photo finish to decide it...Five one-thousandths of a second the difference between gold and silver, and the gold is going to the United States.\\\"\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3424, \"end\": 3437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999970698952165, \"rank\": 2.9172217855009733e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldon on Lyles: \\\"You have got to give this guy credit.\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the talk this year, all the posturing\\u2026He has silenced every single critic.\\\"\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldon on the leadup to the men's 100m: \\\"You could run 100 100m dashes in your life, none of them are going to feel like the pressure and the anticipation and the excitement that you are feeling right now.\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fastest eight men in the world assembled, the whole world stopped, watching who's going to be crowned the world's fastest man.\\\"\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kara Goucher on the men's 1500m semifinals: \\\"3:32.38 for a semi?\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3917, \"end\": 3929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kara_Goucher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kara Goucher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kara_Goucher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kara_Goucher\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we can expect a smoking final.\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 4020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The effortlessness with which those men just ran that.\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is going to be a race for the ages.\\\"\", \"from\": 4076, \"to\": 4117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goucher on Team USA's Yared Nuguse and Hobbs Kessler advancing to the men's 1500m final: \\\"Any doubt that [Yared] Nuguse was nervous or maybe a little overtrained is gone.\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4130, \"end\": 4138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9790500158763906, \"rank\": 0.02139827767270315, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4164, \"end\": 4171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cosmo_Kramer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.552025601831892e-17, \"text\": \"Kessler\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cosmo_Kramer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cosmo_Kramer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is the Nuguse we know.\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He looked great, he controlled that.\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Hobbs Kessler showed that he belongs on this stage and that it was the right decision for him to go pro three years ago [after graduating high school].\\\"\", \"from\": 4355, \"to\": 4511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4365, \"end\": 4372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cosmo_Kramer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.552025601831892e-17, \"text\": \"Kessler\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cosmo_Kramer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cosmo_Kramer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GYMNASTICS  Rich Lerner on Suni Lee: \\\"We have said it throughout the games\\u2026she is a gamer.\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4525, \"end\": 4529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9645434172867017, \"rank\": 0.036759683523454906, \"text\": \"Rich\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 4530, \"end\": 4536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\", \"score\": 0.9998909472951184, \"rank\": 0.00010784359715143022, \"text\": \"Lerner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it's time, she steps up.\\\"\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lerner on Lee winning bronze in the uneven bars: \\\"She has stamped herself as a great American gymnast.\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4646, \"end\": 4649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9349016263506905, \"rank\": 0.06962848251028998, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 4721, \"end\": 4729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996417734000538, \"rank\": 0.000358229846895515, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not just great, but also beloved.\\\"\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lerner on Algerian Kaylia Nemour's uneven bars routine: \\\"We just saw one of the greatest high-pressure performances of these Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first gymnastics medal for Africa.\\\"\", \"from\": 4915, \"to\": 4954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SWIMMING  Dan Hicks on the United States' gold in the women's 4x100m medley relay: \\\"The much talked about gold medal duel between the United States and Australia is officially over and it comes down to the final race to give the Americans the edge, 8-7 over Australia.\\\"\", \"from\": 4956, \"to\": 5225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4966, \"end\": 4975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Hicks_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.7661863309397541, \"rank\": 0.2941348117887413, \"text\": \"Dan Hicks\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Hicks_(singer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Hicks_(singer)\"}, {\"begin\": 4983, \"end\": 4996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999970698952165, \"rank\": 2.9172217855009733e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5018, \"end\": 5037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0910222584422114e-19, \"text\": \"4x100m medley relay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\"}, {\"begin\": 5090, \"end\": 5103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999970698952165, \"rank\": 2.9172217855009733e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5108, \"end\": 5117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9996126409351233, \"rank\": 0.0003873990275303242, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 5214, \"end\": 5223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9996126409351233, \"rank\": 0.0003873990275303242, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rowdy Gaines on Torri Huske anchoring the U.S. women to a gold medal and world record in the women's 4x100m medley relay: \\\"How appropriate is it to have really the best female swimmer for the United States wrap it all up in this gold medal count?\\\"\", \"from\": 5227, \"to\": 5474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5227, \"end\": 5239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rowdy Gaines\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\"}, {\"begin\": 5243, \"end\": 5254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Torri Huske\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\"}, {\"begin\": 5328, \"end\": 5347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0910222584422114e-19, \"text\": \"4x100m medley relay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\"}, {\"begin\": 5419, \"end\": 5432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999970698952165, \"rank\": 2.9172217855009733e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hicks: \\\"Torri Huskehas given every ounce of effort.\\\"\", \"from\": 5476, \"to\": 5528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hicks on Bobby Finke defending his gold medal in the men's 1500m freestyle: \\\"Talk about legends.\", \"from\": 5530, \"to\": 5626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5539, \"end\": 5550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[Katie]Ledeckyknows what Finke has put into this, personally, side by side.\\\"\", \"from\": 5627, \"to\": 5703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaines on Team USA's silver in the men's 4x100 medley relay: \\\"Caeleb Dresselcertainly did his job, all of them did.\", \"from\": 5705, \"to\": 5820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The USA has nothing to hang their heads about... (Dressel) swam with a mighty big heart today.\\\"\", \"from\": 5821, \"to\": 5916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5825, \"end\": 5828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999997700697614, \"rank\": 2.292056106828269e-07, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WOMEN'S BASKETBALL  LaChina Robinson on Team USA women's basketball head coach Cheryl Reeve: \\\"When you talk to the players about Cheryl Reeve's style, they mention three things: toughness, intentional, and defense.\", \"from\": 5918, \"to\": 6132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5958, \"end\": 5966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9790500158763906, \"rank\": 0.02139827767270315, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5997, \"end\": 6009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cheryl Reeve\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\"}, {\"begin\": 6047, \"end\": 6059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cheryl Reeve\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheryl_Reeve\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those are the three things that stand out in terms of her coaching style.\", \"from\": 6133, \"to\": 6206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA has had three different coaches for three different Olympics and each one has been an adjustment.\\\"\", \"from\": 6207, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6207, \"end\": 6210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999997700697614, \"rank\": 2.292056106828269e-07, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GOLF  Steve Sands on Scottie Scheffler winning gold: \\\"Scottie Scheffleradds gold to his green jackets.\\\"\", \"from\": 6311, \"to\": 6414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6317, \"end\": 6328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Sands\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Sands\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Sands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Sands\"}, {\"begin\": 6332, \"end\": 6349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scottie Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sands on Scheffler: \\\"Came here to win a medal, and not just any medal.\", \"from\": 6416, \"to\": 6486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6425, \"end\": 6434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 0.9999999997062332, \"rank\": 2.936126976605765e-10, \"text\": \"Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scottie plays for gold every single week.\\\"\", \"from\": 6487, \"to\": 6529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"John Wood on Great Britain's Tommy Fleetwood's back nine: \\\"Tommy's held it together really well on this backside with the chaos going on with these other two guys in this group falling off the map.\", \"from\": 6531, \"to\": 6728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6531, \"end\": 6540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Wood_(English_actor)\", \"score\": 0.4340829453261457, \"rank\": 0.6446191797719774, \"text\": \"John Wood\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Wood_(English_actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Wood_(English_actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 6544, \"end\": 6557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.7352005212972208, \"rank\": 0.36003750512818355, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's just been very steady.\\\"\", \"from\": 6729, \"to\": 6757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TENNIS  Rennae Stubbs on Novak Djokovic winning gold in men's singles: \\\"This man, the greatest tennis player we have ever seen play this game.\", \"from\": 6759, \"to\": 6901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6784, \"end\": 6798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And for him to finally get this reward of a gold medal - there is been no one that's been more deserving of a gold medal at the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 6902, \"to\": 7040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mary Carillo on the quality of the gold medal match between Djokovic and Carlos Alcaraz: \\\"As riveting a first set as we hoped for.\", \"from\": 7042, \"to\": 7172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7042, \"end\": 7054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Carillo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mary Carillo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Carillo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Carillo\"}, {\"begin\": 7102, \"end\": 7110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999054126, \"rank\": 9.450955048003985e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 7115, \"end\": 7129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hype, the hope, it's being delivered by these two today.\\\"\", \"from\": 7173, \"to\": 7234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stubbs on Djokovic vs. Alcaraz: \\\"I just sit back in awe\\u2026 these guys make tennis look like ping pong\\u2026 this is the best of the best bringing the best.\\\"\", \"from\": 7236, \"to\": 7385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7246, \"end\": 7254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999054126, \"rank\": 9.450955048003985e-11, \"